data.description: Gorgeous Four Bedroom, Two and a Half Bathroom Home in a Desirable Community. First floor has Living Room, Formal Dining Room, Family Room, Kitchen with an Island, Half Bathroom and Laundry Area. There is also a One Car Garage and a nice size Deck. Second Floor has A Large Master Suite, His and Her Closets, Three additional Bedrooms and a Full Bathroom. Did I mention that there are over Three Acres of Land, A Paved Basketball Court with Basketball Hoops? There is also a long Paved Driveway. Low Taxes and Low Dues. Please make haste and schedule your appointment on Showing Time.
